{
  "stem": "11179.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "However, my father had collected enough ads, actually, for two years ahead of time, because he was very friendly with the public relations officer of some of the big companies.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They gave him two year ahead ads.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But he got a commission.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So my father said to the company-- asked the company-- give me 10% of that money so I can leave the country, because he was ready, willing, and able to leave the country in 1933.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they said, no way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We pay you monthly as we take it in, which they did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But so we-- we had no money saved.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Business was pretty bad, as was the-- as-- as-- as the time preceding was bad, like-- like the Depression over here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Over there, it was certainly as bad, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Only the thing was that just-- just prices went up, and up, and up, and people didn't have any money, so it amounted to the same thing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so I got a scholarship still, in the spring of 1933, when I went to started going [INAUDIBLE] the high school.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they cancelled that scholarship, but they told me, since my father was a veteran of World War I, they would-- I could stay.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But it cost so-- so much a month, and it was a considerable amount.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I believe it was 35 Marks, something like this-- the full amount, not even reduced.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So my father took me out of the school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] my father was teaching at a private Jewish school, and they got me in there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a-- a-- advertising salesman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, he was selling the ads to the big companies.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had big-- lots of big ads in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
